<item>
 <title>VILAS MED INTRODUCTION	</title>
 <link>http://boa.gov.vn/en/vilas-med-introduction</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-dichvu-phamvi field-type-markup field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-dichvu-noi-dung field-type-text-long field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;VIETNAM ACCREDITATION SCHEME FOR MEDICAL TESTING LABORATORY (VILAS MED)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
One of accreditation schemes of BoA
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Organization and operation conform with the&amp;nbsp; requirements of ISO/IEC 17011:2004, ILAC, APLAC related documents and other international organizations&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Medical testing laboratory imply medical laboratory and imaging laboratory&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The accreditation criteria for medical laboratory: ISO 15189:2012 (TCVN 15189:2014) “Medical laboratories – Particular requirements for quality and competence” and supplementary requirements for specific medical testing as its accreditation criteria&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Scope of medical tests include: clinical chemistry; hematology; clinical microbiology; pathology and cyto-pathology; medical nuclear; imaging testing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Benefit of accreditation&lt;/strong&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Improving management and technical performance for medical laboratory;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Permission to use the accreditation stamp and logo on medical test report;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Enhancing image and competitive advantages in Vietnam and the world;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The users can select the accredited medical laboratory who are independent, impartial and competent.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
